{"id": 6551, "title": "Ticket #6551: Remove check for CurrentTime attribute when sending classads", "description": "<blockquote>\nIn the old classads days, we'd add an attribute\n\n<p><span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=CurrentTime\" title=\"Current Time\">CurrentTime</a></span> = time()\n\n</p><p>in all classads.  In the transition to new classads, we don't need to do this, but for compatability reasons, if an in-memory classad has this attribute, we remove it before sending it on the wire, which is relatively expensive.  Let's expunge this now-unneeded code.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2018-Mar-09 16:04</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/e1567bb1305816c8c619b15b87a81f04436b61c5\">[54480]</a></span>: Reorder version history, fix typos, add history for <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=6550\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6550'); return false;\" title=\"Don't use sprintf to format classad integer values for cedar\">#6550</a></span> <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=6551\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6551'); return false;\" title=\"Remove check for CurrentTime attribute when sending classads\">#6551</a></span> <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=6565\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6565'); return false;\" title=\"Remove duplicate strlen calls in cedar\">#6565</a></span> <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets